    <item>
      <title>西班牙对德意志银行罚款1000万欧元，以销售衍生品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/spain-fines-deutsche-bank-10-million-over-sale-of-derivatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行（Deutsche Bank AG）被西班牙的证券监管机构CNMV罚款1000万欧元（1,030万美元），因为他们向客户出售衍生品，后来表示他们不了解这些产品，因此遭受了巨大的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/spain-fines-deutsche-bank-10-million-over-sale-of-derivatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:11:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希思罗机场以更快地揭示扩张速度，誓言优先考虑英国钢铁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/heathrow-to-announce-faster-expansion-vow-to-prioritze-uk-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦的希思罗机场机场（Heathrow Airport）将发布一项短期扩张计划，包括及时承诺优先考虑英国钢铁受到美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）关税的威胁，并在建立第三条跑道之前为枢纽提供了潜在的提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/heathrow-to-announce-faster-expansion-vow-to-prioritze-uk-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:04:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普建议马诺在国库中发现不规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-10/trump-suggests-doge-found-irregularities-at-treasury-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统建议，埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的政府效率团队在检查美国财政部的数据时发现了违规行为，并暗示这可能导致美国无视一些付款。彭博的迈克·谢泼德（Mike Shepard）报道。  （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-10/trump-suggests-doge-found-irregularities-at-treasury-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 16:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>机构说，监管负担拖延了加拿大的经济增长。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/regulatory-burden-drags-down-canada-s-economic-growth-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国中央统计局说，规则和法规的数量增加降低了近2个百分点，从加拿大业务部门的产出增长在15年内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/regulatory-burden-drags-down-canada-s-economic-growth-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 16:50:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的Lagarde说，在轨道上解散，但贸易构成风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/ecb-s-lagarde-says-disinflation-on-track-but-trade-poses-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲中央银行总裁克里斯汀·拉加德（Christine Lagarde）表示，尽管全球贸易摩擦继续构成风险，但通货膨胀的撤退正在进行中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/ecb-s-lagarde-says-disinflation-on-track-but-trade-poses-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 16:43:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安大略省说，它将禁止中国与矿物质，能源交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/ontario-says-it-would-ban-china-from-deals-on-minerals-energy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大省的领导人表示，如果本月晚些时候再次当选他的政党，政府将禁止中国组成部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/ontario-says-it-would-ban-china-from-deals-on-minerals-energy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 16:38:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷德伍德（Redwood）的43亿美元信贷基金在阿根廷获得17％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/redwood-s-4-3-billion-credit-fund-gains-17-on-argentina-dish</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社的一份投资者的信件，去年，Redwood Capital Management的主要基金去年获得了约17％的收益，这是由赌注，石化生产商TPC集团和卫星电视提供商Dish Network在内的不良信贷驱动的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/redwood-s-4-3-billion-credit-fund-gains-17-on-argentina-dish</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 16:35:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利公司向亲俄罗斯摩尔多瓦地区提供汽油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/hungarian-company-to-supply-gas-to-pro-russian-moldova-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦总理说，匈牙利的气体和能源营销将在摩尔多瓦总理拒绝进一步的欧盟援助之后，将为摩尔多瓦亲俄罗斯地区的特兰斯特里亚地区提供天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/hungarian-company-to-supply-gas-to-pro-russian-moldova-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 12:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普放大贸易言论时，美元增加了收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/dollar-advances-on-trump-s-steel-comment-as-trade-jitters-deepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，投资者赶到避风港资料，购买了美元和黄金，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）威胁要对钢铁和铝进口征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/dollar-advances-on-trump-s-steel-comment-as-trade-jitters-deepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 23:08:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票随着黄金命中纪录高高而获得技术提升：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/commodity-currencies-slide-on-trump-tariff-plans-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票在一周的上升开始，在对通货膨胀和美国关税威胁的担忧驱动的幻灯片推动下，股票反弹。美元加强和黄金创下了创纪录的纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/commodity-currencies-slide-on-trump-tariff-plans-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 22:38:27 GMT</pubDate>
